      "content": "Trigger and cancel notification workflows, and inspect workflow recipient runs. Workflows are Knock's core programmable notification model — orchestrating channel steps (email, SMS, push, in-app, chat), function steps (batch, delay, branch, throttle, fetch, AI agent), and conditions across recipients.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Knock",
